# Frontend API Guide (Next.js + fetch) - comvia

Tài liệu này hướng dẫn FE Next.js gọi backend NestJS theo các API hiện có trong dự án `e-Nest-comvia`.

## 1) Base URL & Environments

### 1.1 Biến môi trường gợi ý
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` (vd: `http://localhost:3000`)
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_DEMO_MODE` (tùy bạn; backend đọc `DEMO_MODE` ở server)

Ví dụ `.env.local` (Next.js):
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3000"
```

## 2) Chuẩn hóa cách gọi API bằng fetch

### 2.1 Helper `comviaFetch`
Bạn có thể copy trực tiếp theo kiểu TS:
```ts
// app/lib/comviaFetch.ts
export type ComviaApiError = {
  statusCode?: number;
  message?: string | string[];
  error?: string;
};

function readJsonSafe<T>(res: Response): Promise<T | null> {
  const ct = res.headers.get("content-type") ?? "";
  if (!ct.includes("application/json")) return Promise.resolve(null);
  return res.json().catch(() => null);
}

export async function comviaFetch<T>(
  path: string,
  init?: RequestInit & { apiKey?: string; token?: string },
): Promise<T> {
  const baseUrl = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL;
  if (!baseUrl) throw new Error("Missing NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL");

  const url = `${baseUrl}${path}`;

  const headers = new Headers(init?.headers);
  headers.set("Content-Type", "application/json");

  if (init?.token) headers.set("Authorization", `Bearer ${init.token}`);
  if (init?.apiKey) {
    // backend Public API có thể đọc x-api-key (hoặc body/query api_key)
    headers.set("x-api-key", init.apiKey);
  }

  const res = await fetch(url, {
    ...init,
    headers,
  });

  if (!res.ok) {
    const data = await readJsonSafe<ComviaApiError>(res);
    const msg =
      (typeof data?.message === "string" && data.message) ||
      (Array.isArray(data?.message) && data.message.join(", ")) ||
      data?.error ||
      `HTTP ${res.status}`;

    throw new Error(msg);
  }

  return (await res.json()) as T;
}
```

### 2.2 Format body chung
- Backend NestJS đang dùng `ValidationPipe` nên body phải đúng field/type theo DTO.
- Tất cả ví dụ dưới đây dùng JSON `Content-Type: application/json`.

## 3) JWT Auth (Login / Me / OTP)

### 3.1 Register (OTP demo)

Endpoint:
- `POST /auth/register` (Public)

Request:
```json
{
  "email": "demo.user@example.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "fullName": "Demo User"
}
```

Response (khi `DEMO_MODE=true`):
```json
{
  "id": "USER_ID",
  "email": "demo.user@example.com",
  "fullName": "Demo User",
  "role": "USER",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-20T07:..Z",
  "otpRequestId": "OTP_REQUEST_ID",
  "expiredAt": "2026-03-20T07:..Z",
  "demoOtpCode": "123456"
}
```

Ghi chú:
- Sau register, user ở trạng thái `PENDING_VERIFICATION`.
- Bạn phải gọi `otp/verify` trước khi `login` được.

FE call ví dụ:
```ts
const registerRes = await comviaFetch<any>("/auth/register", {
  method: "POST",
  body: JSON.stringify({ email, password, fullName }),
});
const otpCode = registerRes.demoOtpCode; // chỉ có khi DEMO_MODE=true
```

### 3.2 Verify OTP (đổi sang ACTIVE + nhận accessToken)

Endpoint:
- `POST /auth/otp/verify` (Public)

Request:
```json
{
  "targetType": "EMAIL",
  "targetValue": "demo.user@example.com",
  "purpose": "REGISTER",
  "otpCode": "123456"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "accessToken": "JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN",
  "tokenType": "Bearer",
  "user": {
    "id": "USER_ID",
    "email": "demo.user@example.com",
    "fullName": "Demo User",
    "role": "USER",
    "status": "ACTIVE"
  }
}
```

### 3.3 Login

Endpoint:
- `POST /auth/login` (Public)

Request:
```json
{
  "email": "demo.user@example.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "accessToken": "JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN",
  "tokenType": "Bearer",
  "user": {
    "id": "USER_ID",
    "email": "demo.user@example.com",
    "fullName": "Demo User",
    "role": "USER"
  }
}
```

### 3.4 Me

Endpoint:
- `GET /auth/me`

Headers:
- `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>`

Response:
```json
{
  "id": "USER_ID",
  "email": "demo.user@example.com",
  "fullName": "Demo User",
  "role": "USER",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-20T07:..Z"
}
```

### 3.5 Update my profile

Endpoint:
- `PATCH /users/me`

Headers:
- `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>`

Request:
```json
{
  "fullName": "Demo User Updated"
}
```

## 4) Workspace APIs (cốt lõi cho mọi nghiệp vụ)

Tất cả route workspace hiện đang theo pattern:
- `/workspaces/:workspaceId/...`

### 4.1 Create workspace (OWNER)
Endpoint:
- `POST /workspaces`

Headers:
- JWT

Request:
```json
{
  "name": "Demo Workspace",
  "slug": "demo-workspace",
  "billing": {
    "billingType": "ORGANIZATION",
    "companyName": "Demo Company",
    "taxCode": "0312345678",
    "address": "123 Demo Street",
    "invoiceEmail": "billing@demo.com",
    "representativeName": "Nguyen Van A",
    "phone": "0901234567"
  }
}
```

Hoặc loại `INDIVIDUAL`:
```json
{
  "name": "Demo Workspace",
  "slug": "demo-workspace",
  "billing": {
    "billingType": "INDIVIDUAL",
    "fullName": "Nguyen Van B",
    "citizenId": "079123456789",
    "taxCode": "8561234567",
    "address": "123 Demo Street",
    "invoiceEmail": "demo.user@example.com",
    "phone": "0901234567"
  }
}
```

Response (tối giản):
```json
{
  "id": "WS_ID",
  "name": "Demo Workspace",
  "slug": "demo-workspace",
  "ownerUserId": "USER_ID",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "createdAt": "...",
  "billingProfile": {
    "billingType": "ORGANIZATION",
    "companyName": "Demo Company",
    "taxCode": "0312345678",
    "address": "123 Demo Street",
    "invoiceEmail": "billing@demo.com"
  }
}
```

### 4.2 List my workspaces
Endpoint:
- `GET /workspaces`

Response:
```json
[
  {
    "id": "WS_ID",
    "name": "Demo Workspace",
    "slug": "demo-workspace",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "role": "OWNER",
    "joinedAt": "..."
  }
]
```

### 4.3 Switch workspace
Endpoint:
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/switch`

Response:
```json
{ "id": "USER_ID", "lastActiveWorkspaceId": "WS_ID" }
```

