## 6) OA Connection (mock)

Endpoint:
- `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/oa/status`
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/oa/connect` (OWNER)
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/oa/disconnect` (OWNER)

Các API này hiện dùng mock OA. Frontend chỉ cần gọi connect trước khi làm Template/Messaging (vì backend check `oa.status === CONNECTED`).

## 7) Templates (CRUD + submit + staff approve/reject)

Base:
- `/workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`

### 7.1 Create template
Auth/Role: `OWNER` hoặc `MEMBER`

Endpoint:
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`

Request (không gửi `code`; backend tự sinh):
```json
{
  "name": "Template Demo",
  "content": "<zns>..</zns>",
  "placeholdersJson": { "name": "string" }
}
```

Ghi chú:
- `code` do backend gán khi tạo: chuỗi **6 chữ số**, random trong khoảng **100000–999999**, **unique trong workspace**. Frontend lấy `code` từ **response** của `POST` (cùng các field như list/get).

### 7.2 List templates
- `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`

### 7.3 Get template
- `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId`

### 7.4 Update template
- `PATCH /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId`

Ghi chú:
- Backend chặn sửa khi template đã `APPROVED`.

### 7.5 Submit template
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId/submit`

Response hiện tại là cập nhật trạng thái sang `PENDING_ZALO_APPROVAL` (mock flow).

### 7.6 Staff review APIs (internal)
Base:
- `/internal/templates`
- `/internal/templates/:templateId`
- `/internal/templates/:templateId/mark-pending-zalo-approval`
- `/internal/templates/:templateId/approve`
- `/internal/templates/:templateId/reject`
- `/internal/templates/:templateId/disable`

Auth/Role: `STAFF` (UserRole.STAFF)

List queue:
```http
GET /internal/templates?status=SUBMITTED&keyword=demo&limit=20
```

List response (tối giản):
```json
[
  {
    "id": "TEMPLATE_ID",
    "name": "Template Demo",
    "code": "482391",
    "status": "SUBMITTED",
    "workspace": {
      "id": "WS_ID",
      "name": "Demo Workspace",
      "slug": "demo-workspace",
      "status": "ACTIVE"
    },
    "oaConnection": {
      "id": "OA_CONN_ID",
      "oaId": "OA_123",
      "oaName": "Demo OA",
      "status": "CONNECTED"
    }
  }
]
```

Detail:
```http
GET /internal/templates/:templateId
```

Mark pending zalo approval:
```http
POST /internal/templates/:templateId/mark-pending-zalo-approval
```

Approve request:
```json
{ "providerTemplateId": "ZALO_TPL_123" }
```

Reject request:
```json
{ "reason": "Rejected for demo" }
```

Disable:
```http
POST /internal/templates/:templateId/disable
```

Sau khi approve xong, template trở thành `APPROVED` để FE có thể gửi message.

## 8) Messaging (send single + logs) - mock provider

Base:
- `/workspaces/:workspaceId/messages`

### 8.1 Send single
Auth/Role: `OWNER` hoặc `MEMBER`

Endpoint:
- `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/messages/send-single`

Request:
```json
{
  "templateId": "TEMPLATE_ID",
  "phoneNumber": "84901234567",
  "data": { "name": "Minh" }
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "providerMessageId": "mock_msg_...",
  "messageLogId": "MESSAGE_LOG_ID"
}
```

### 8.2 List message logs
Endpoint:
- `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/messages/logs?status=SUCCESS&sendType=SINGLE&limit=50`

Query:
- `status` (MessageStatus)
- `sendType` (SendType)
- `limit` (optional)

